QuestData.Title: Ominous Portents
QuestData.Description: Now that Priestess Moonfang has created the blessed water, it is time to deal with the demon.$B$BTake the water and the scripture of Elune.$B$BThrough the power of each, you will compel the demon to show us what the orcs are up to at Gul'var.
QuestData.CompletionText: The demon must be put to the test if we're to find out what's happening at Gul'var.
QuestData.RewardText: Gul'dan is there! We must move quickly to capture him.
